<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Document</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/bootstrap/5.3.3/css/bootstrap.min.css" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.7.2/css/all.min.css"  />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/fancybox/3.5.7/jquery.fancybox.min.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/Swiper/8.1.6/swiper-bundle.min.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/flatpickr/4.6.13/flatpickr.min.css" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/aos/2.3.4/aos.css" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="css/styles.css">
    <style  nonce="<%= nonce %>">
        /* General Reset */
* {
    margin: 0;
    padding: 0;
    box-sizing: border-box;
}

html {
    scroll-behavior: smooth; 
}

body {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    overflow-x: hidden;
    color: #000;
    background: #fff;
}

.section-title {
    position: relative;
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 40px;  /* Space between title and grid */
    padding: 0 20px; /* Add padding for better spacing on small devices */
}

.section-title  {
    font-size: 2rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 1px;
    color: #fff;
    position: relative;
    margin: 0;
    padding: 0;
}

/* Before and After Effects for Section Title */
.section-title::before,
.section-title::after {
    content: "";
    position: absolute;
    top: 50%;
    width: 20%;
    height: 1px;
    background-color: #333;
    transform: translateY(-50%);
}

.section-title::before {
    left: 0;
}

.section-title::after {
    right: 0;
}

/* Optional decorative flair */
.section-title::before {
    background-image: linear-gradient(45deg, #ff7e5f, #feb47b);
    background-size: 100% 2px;
}

.section-title::after {
    background-image: linear-gradient(45deg, #ff7e5f, #feb47b);
    background-size: 100% 2px;
}

/* Make the title lines responsive */
@media (max-width: 768px) {
    .section-title {
        font-size: 1.5rem;  /* Smaller font size for mobile */
    }

    .section-title::before,
    .section-title::after {
        width: 15%;  /* Shorten the lines for smaller screens */
    }
}

img {
  object-fit: cover;
}

.toast {
    max-width: 400px;
    opacity: 0.9;
    font-size: 1rem;
    background-color: #28a745;
    color: white;
}

.toast-header {
    background-color: #218838;
}

.toast-body {
    background-color: #28a745;
}

.toast-body small {
    color: #fff;
}

/* navigation */
.sticky-navbar {
    position: sticky;
    top: 0;
    z-index: 999;
    width: 100%;
    background: rgba(32, 31, 31, 0.932);
}


.navbar {
    width: 100%;
    z-index: 998; 
    padding: 10px;
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: center;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
}

.navbar-container {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: space-between;
    width: 100%;
    background: rgba(32, 31, 31, 0.932);
}

.navbar .logo a {
    font-size: 32px;
    color: white;
    font-weight: bold;
    letter-spacing: 1px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    text-decoration: none;
}

.navbar-menu ul {
    list-style: none;
    display: flex;
    gap: 30px;
}

.navbar-menu a {
    color: white;
    font-size: 18px;
    text-decoration: none;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    transition: 0.3s ease;
    position: relative;
}

.navbar-menu a::after {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    bottom: -4px;
    left: 50%;
    width: 0;
    height: 2px;
    background: linear-gradient(45deg, #ff0080, #ff8c00);
    transition: 0.3s ease;
    transform: translateX(-50%);
}

.navbar-menu a:hover::after {
    width: 100%;
}


.sidebar {
    position: fixed;
    top: 0;
    left: -300px;
    height: 100%;
    width: 300px;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #130f0f, #161616);
    transition: left 0.3s ease;
    z-index: 9999;
}

.sidebar.open {
    left: 0;
}

.sidebar-content {
    padding: 50px 20px;
}

.sidebar-content h3 {
    color: #fff;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 1px;
}

.sidebar ul {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
}

.sidebar ul li {
    padding: 15px 0;
    border-bottom: 1px solid #fff;
}

.sidebar ul li a {
    color: #fff;
    text-decoration: none;
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    transition: color 0.3s ease;
}

.sidebar ul li a:hover {
    color: #000;
}

#sidebar-close {
    position: absolute;
    top: 20px;
    right: 20px;
    color: white;
    font-size: 2rem;
    cursor: pointer;
    z-index: 9999;
}

#hamburger-toggle {
    background: none;
    border: none;
    color: #fff;
    font-size: 2rem;
    padding: 10px;
    cursor: pointer;
    display: none;
}

@media (max-width: 768px) {
    .navbar-menu {
        display: none;
    }

    #hamburger-toggle {
        display: block;
    }

    .sidebar.open {
        left: 0;
    }

    body, html {
        overflow-x: hidden;
    }
}


/* Hero Section */
.hero-section {
    height: 100vh;
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    align-items: center;
    flex-direction: column;
    position: relative;
    overflow: visible;
    color: white;
    text-align: center;
}

.hero-content {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    text-align: center;
    height: 100vh;
    color: white;
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1000;
}

.hero-text {
    max-width: 600px;
    padding: 20px;
}

.tagline {
    font-size: 1rem;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 2px;
    color: #1d0ea0;
    font-weight: bold;
    display: block;
    margin-bottom: 10px;
}

h1 {
    font-size: 4rem;
    font-weight: bold;
    margin-bottom: 15px;
    line-height: 1.2;
}

.subtext {
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    opacity: 0.8;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
}

.button-group {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: 15px;
    margin-top: 20px;
}

.cta-button, .secondary-button {
    padding: 12px 20px;
    font-size: 1rem;
    font-weight: bold;
    text-decoration: none;
    border-radius: 8px;
    transition: all 0.3s ease-in-out;
}

.cta-button {
    background: linear-gradient(45deg, #0a1ed1, #048bc0);
    color: white;
    border: none;
}

.cta-button:hover {
    background: linear-gradient(45deg, #048bc0, #0a1ed1);
    transform: scale(1.05);
}

.secondary-button {
    background: transparent;
    border: 2px solid white;
    color: white;
}

.secondary-button:hover {
    background: white;
    color: black;
    transform: scale(1.05);
}

/* Parallax Image */
.paroller-container {
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    left: 0;
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    z-index: 1;
    overflow: hidden;
}

.dim-color {
  position: absolute;
  left: 0;
  right: 0;
  content: "";
  width: 100%;
  height: 100%;
  background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);
  z-index: 2;
}

.paroller-image,
.paroller-image-second {
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    left: 50%;
    width: 200%; 
    height: 100%;
    transform: translateX(-50%); /* Center the image */
}


.paroller-image img,
.paroller-image-second img {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    object-fit: cover;
}


/* Media Queries for Responsiveness */
@media (max-width: 768px) {
    .hero-section h1 {
        font-size: 2.5rem;
    }

    .hero-section p {
        font-size: 1rem;
    }

    .cta-button {
        font-size: 1rem;
    }
}

.page-hero-header {
    width: 100%;
    min-height: 100%;
    padding-top: 2rem;
    background: url(" /images/hero-3.jpg");
    background-position: center;
    background-size: cover;
    object-fit: cover;
  }

  .dim-bg-color {
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    top: 0;
    content: "";
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    background: #33333383;
  }


  .search-container {
    position: absolute;
    bottom: 0;
    left: 50%;
    transform: translateX(-50%) translateY(50%);
    width: 100%;
    max-width: 1200px;
    padding: 20px;
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.80);
    box-shadow: 0px 10px 30px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
    border-radius: 12px;
    backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    box-sizing: border-box;
    z-index: 1000; 
}

/* Ensure the next section doesn't hide the search container */
.next-section {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
    height: 50px;
}

/* Ensure the form wrapper fits within the container */
.form-wrapper {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 20px;
    width: 100%;
    box-sizing: border-box;
    justify-content: space-between;
}


/* Form Layout */
.tm-booking-form {
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
    padding: 20px;
    border-radius: 12px;
    backdrop-filter: blur(8px);
    box-shadow: 0px 5px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
    transition: transform 0.3s ease-in-out;
    flex: 1;
    min-width: 280px;
    max-width: 100%;
    box-sizing: border-box;
}

/* Hover Effect */
.tm-booking-form:hover {
    transform: translateY(-5px);
}

/* Flex Row Layout for Inputs & Button */
.form-row {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 15px;
    width: 100%;
    flex-direction: row; /* Keep horizontal layout by default */
}

/* Form Group Styling */
.form-group {
    flex: 1 1 200px;
    box-sizing: border-box;
    position: relative;
}

/* Labels */
.form-label {
    font-size: 14px;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: #000;
    margin-bottom: 5px;
}

/* Inputs & Selects Styling */
.form-control {
    width: 100%;
    padding: 12px 14px;
    border: 1px solid rgba(19, 231, 235, 0.5);
    border-radius: 8px;
    font-size: 16px;
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
    color: #000;
    transition: 0.3s;
    box-sizing: border-box;
}

/* Style dropdown options */
.form-control option {
    background-color: white; /* Default background */
    color: #333; /* Default text color */
    font-size: 1rem;
    padding: 10px; /* Space inside options */
}

/* Hover effect for options (Some browsers may not support it) */
.form-control option:hover {
    background-color: #3498db; /* Highlight color */
    color: white;
}

/* Style the selected option */
.form-control option:checked {
    background-color: #2ecc71; /* Green for selected */
    color: white;
    font-weight: bold;
}

.form-control:focus {
    border-color: #00c6ff;
    box-shadow: 0px 0px 8px rgba(0, 198, 255, 0.6);
    outline: none;
}

 /* Hide the default select dropdown */
 .custom-dropdown {
        position: relative;
        width: 100%;
    }

    .custom-dropdown .selected {
        background: white;
        color: #000;
        border: 2px solid #3498db;
        padding: 12px;
        font-size: 1rem;
        border-radius: 5px;
        cursor: pointer;
        display: flex;
        justify-content: space-between;
        align-items: center;
    }

    /* Dropdown list */
    .custom-dropdown .dropdown-list {
        position: absolute;
        width: 100%;
        background: white;
        color: #000;
        border: 2px solid #3498db;
        border-top: none;
        display: none;
        z-index: 1000;
        border-radius: 5px;
    }

    .custom-dropdown.active .dropdown-list {
        display: block;
    }

    .custom-dropdown .dropdown-list div {
        padding: 10px;
        cursor: pointer;
        font-size: 1rem;
        transition: 0.3s;
        border-bottom: 1px solid #ddd;
    }

    .custom-dropdown .dropdown-list div:last-child {
        border-bottom: none;
    }

    .custom-dropdown .dropdown-list div:hover {
        background: #3498db;
        color: white;
    }

/* Position the Calendar Icon */
.input-icon {
    position: absolute;
    right: 15px;
    top: 50%;
    transform: translateY(-50%);
    color: rgba(48, 17, 223, 0.7);
    pointer-events: none;
}

/* Button Styling */
button.btn {
    padding: 12px 20px;
    background: linear-gradient(90deg, #00c6ff, #0072ff);
    color: white;
    font-size: 16px;
    font-weight: bold;
    border: none;
    border-radius: 8px;
    cursor: pointer;
    transition: 0.3s ease-in-out;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    min-width: 150px;
    box-sizing: border-box;
}

button.btn:hover {
    background: linear-gradient(90deg, #0072ff, #00c6ff);
    box-shadow: 0px 5px 15px rgba(0, 198, 255, 0.3);
    transform: scale(1.05);
}

/* Responsive Design */
@media (max-width: 768px) {
    .search-container {
        display: none;
    }
}

/* about section */
.s-image {
    transform: translateY(-60%);
    background: #fff;
}

/* Room gallery */
/* Room Gallery Section */
.room-gallery {
  background: #f8f9fa;
}

.room-card {
  position: relative;
  border-radius: 12px;
  overflow: hidden;
  box-shadow: 0px 4px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
  transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;
  cursor: pointer;
}

.room-card:hover {
  transform: translateY(-5px);
  box-shadow: 0px 6px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
}

.room-image {
  width: 100%;
  height: 250px;
  object-fit: cover;
  transition: transform 0.3s ease;
}

.room-card:hover .room-image {
  transform: scale(1.05);
}

/* Overlay for Description */
.room-overlay {
  position: absolute;
  bottom: 0;
  left: 0;
  width: 100%;
  background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.7);
  color: white;
  padding: 15px;
  text-align: center;
  transform: translateY(100%);
  transition: transform 0.4s ease-in-out;
}

.room-card:hover .room-overlay {
  transform: translateY(0);
}

.room-overlay h4 {
  font-size: 1.3rem;
  font-weight: 600;
  margin-bottom: 5px;
}

.room-overlay p {
  font-size: 1rem;
  margin: 0;
  opacity: 0.9;
}

/* Swiper Navigation Buttons */
.swiper-button-next,
.swiper-button-prev {
  color: #007bff !important;
  transition: 0.3s ease;
}

.swiper-button-next:hover,
.swiper-button-prev:hover {
  color: #0056b3 !important;
}

    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <%- include("../partials/_nav.ejs") %>
    <!-- Hero Section -->
    <section class="hero-section">
        <div class="dim-color"></div>
        <div class="paroller-container">
            <div class="paroller-image">
                <img src="/images/hero-2.jpg" alt="Hero Background" />
            </div>
            <div class="paroller-image-second">
                <img src="/images/hero-2.jpg" alt="Second Background" />
            </div>
        </div>
    
        <div class="hero-content">
            <div class="hero-text">
                <span class="tagline" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="500" >A Cozy Escape Awaits</span>
                <h1 class="section-title-icon" data-aos="flip-left" data-aos-easing="ease-out-cubic" data-aos-delay="500" data-aos-duration="2000">
                  <i class="fa-regular fa-star"></i>
                  <i class="fa-regular fa-star"></i>
                  Buffalo Lodge
                  <i class="fa-regular fa-star"></i>
                  <i class="fa-regular fa-star"></i>
                </h1>
                <p class="subtext" data-aos="fade-down" data-aos-delay="500" >Experience Comfort, Tranquility, and Warm Hospitality.</p>
                <div class="button-group">
                    <a href="/contact" class="cta-button" data-aos="fade-up-right" data-aos-delay="500" >Get in Touch</a>
                    <a href="/about" class="secondary-button" data-aos="fade-up-left" data-aos-delay="500">Learn More</a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>  
        <div class="search-container">
            <div class="form-wrapper">
                <!-- First Form (Room Selection & Month) -->
                <form action="/availability" method="GET" class="tm-booking-form">
                    <div class="form-row">
                        <div class="form-group">
                            <select name="roomNumber" id="roomNumber" class="form-control" required>
                                <% rooms.forEach(room => { %>
                                    <option value="<%= room.roomNumber %>">Room <%= room.roomNumber %> (Capacity: <%= room.capacity %>)</option>
                                <% }); %>
                            </select>
                        </div>
        
                        <div class="form-group">
                            <select name="month" id="month" class="form-control" required>
                                <% for(let i = 1; i <= 12; i++) { %>
                                    <option value="<%= i %>"><%= new Date(2025, i - 1, 1).toLocaleString('default', { month: 'long' }) %></option>
                                <% } %>
                            </select>
                            <i class="fas fa-calendar-alt input-icon"></i>
                        </div>
        
                        <input type="hidden" name="year" value="2025">
                        <button type="submit" class="btn">Room Availability</button>
                    </div>
                </form>
        
                <!-- Second Form (Check-in & Check-out) -->
                <form action="/search-rooms" method="get" class="tm-booking-form">
                    <div class="form-row">
                        <div class="form-group">
                            <input type="text" class="form-control datefield" name="checkInDate" id="inputCheckIn" placeholder="Check In" readonly>
                            <i class="fas fa-calendar-alt input-icon"></i>
                        </div>
                        <div class="form-group">
                            <input type="text" class="form-control datefield" name="checkOutDate" id="inputCheckOut" placeholder="Check Out" readonly>
                            <i class="fas fa-calendar-alt input-icon"></i>
                        </div>
        
                        <button type="submit" class="btn">Check Availability</button>
                    </div>
                </form>    
            </div>
        </div>     
    </section>
    <div class="next-section"></div>

    <div class="container-xxl py-5 mt-5">
        <div class="container">
          <div class="row g-5">
            <div class="col-lg-6" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="100">
              <div class="d-flex flex-column position-relative">
                <img class="img-fluid rounded w-75 align-self-end f-image" src="/images/hero-1.jpg" alt="Guesthouse image">
                <img class="img-fluid rounded w-50 pt-3 pe-3 s-image" src="/images/hero-1.jpg" alt="Guesthouse image" style="position: absolute; top: 55%; left: 10%; margin-top:-25%;">
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-lg-6" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="500">
              <h2 class="mb-4 text-black">Welcome to 
                <span class="section-title welcome-title">Buffalo Lodge</span></h1>
              <p class="mb-4 fs-5 text-muted">At our guesthouse, we strive to provide a comfortable and memorable experience for all our guests. From cozy rooms to top-notch amenities, we ensure that your stay is special.</p>
              <p class="mb-4 fs-5 text-muted">We offer affordable accommodation, excellent service, and a variety of facilities to meet all your needs during your stay. Whether you're here for a relaxing vacation or a business trip, we have everything you need.</p>
              <a class="btn btn-primary rounded-pill py-3 px-5 mt-3" href="/about">Read More</a>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <section class="amenities-section py-5 position-relative">
        <div class="dim-bg-color"></div>
        <div class="container">
          <h2 class="text-center mb-5 fw-bold section-title z-3">Amenities</h2>
          <div class="row g-4 z-3">
            <div class="col-md-6 col-lg-4" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="100">
              <div class="amenity-card">
                <div class="icon"><i class="fas fa-wifi"></i></div>
                <h4>Free Wi-Fi</h4>
                <p>Enjoy high-speed internet access throughout our guesthouse, ensuring you're always connected.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
      
            <div class="col-md-6 col-lg-4" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="200">
              <div class="amenity-card">
                <div class="icon"><i class="fas fa-utensils"></i></div>
                <h4>Complimentary Breakfast</h4>
                <p>Start your day with a fresh, delicious breakfast included with your stay.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
      
            <div class="col-md-6 col-lg-4" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="300">
              <div class="amenity-card">
                <div class="icon"><i class="fas fa-swimmer"></i></div>
                <h4>Swimming Pool</h4>
                <p>Relax and unwind in our beautiful outdoor swimming pool, available for all guests.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
      
            <div class="col-md-6 col-lg-4" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="400">
              <div class="amenity-card">
                <div class="icon"><i class="fas fa-parking"></i></div>
                <h4>Free Parking</h4>
                <p>Convenient on-site parking is available at no additional cost for our guests.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
      
            <div class="col-md-6 col-lg-4" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="500">
              <div class="amenity-card">
                <div class="icon"><i class="fas fa-dumbbell"></i></div>
                <h4>Fitness Center</h4>
                <p>Stay active with our well-equipped gym, open 24/7 for guest use.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
      
            <div class="col-md-6 col-lg-4" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="600">
              <div class="amenity-card">
                <div class="icon"><i class="fas fa-concierge-bell"></i></div>
                <h4>24/7 Front Desk</h4>
                <p>Our friendly staff is available around the clock to assist you with anything you need.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
      
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>



      <section class="room-gallery">
       <div class="container">
        <h2 class="section-title text-black">Our Room Gallery</h2>
        <div class="room-display-container mt-5">
          <!-- Room Display Block 1 -->
          <div class="room-display-block">
            <div class="room-image-gallery">
